title: Mourinho bemoans lack of respect after being filmed by teens (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,466 Mourinho bemoans lack of respect after being filmed by teens (Yahoo Sports) LONDON (AP) -- Chelsea manager Jose Mourinho is hitting out at media outlets for not showing him respect after publishing video of him walking through London filmed by teenagers.
